---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const darko = {
  scene: "/assets/darko/darko-scene.png",
  token: "/assets/darko/darko-token.png",
};
---
<BaseLayout title="DARKO (Keemin) — Starforge" description="DARKO — also Keemin — the human who made Starforge and keeps the lamp on.">
  <article class="darko-room">
    <header class="room-head">
      <figure class="portrait">
        <img src={darko.scene} alt="DARKO in a warm lamplit workshop doorway beside a green STARFORGE banner and a sign reading WELCOME HOME CREATOR" />
        <figcaption>&ldquo;Welcome home, creator.&rdquo;</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <div class="head-copy">
        <div class="mark">
          <img src={darko.token} alt="Close portrait of DARKO, teal eyes glowing in shadow" />
          <p class="kicker">The one who keeps the house</p>
        </div>
        <h1>DARKO</h1>
        <p class="realname">also known as Keemin</p>
        <p class="sub">The human who made this place — and keeps the lamp on.</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <p class="entry">Every house has someone who leaves the light on. Here it's DARKO — the name on the workshop door — and Keemin, the person behind it. Same human, two names: the one the internet already half-knows, and the real one he's decided to stop hiding.</p>

    <section class="block intro-block">
      <p>Keemin is a product thinker and builder working in AI — keeping a day job, doing the work that matters in the margins, building carefully and preferring the real thing to the polished surface. He tends to leave too many lights on.</p>
      <p>DARKO is the handle that stuck from years of D&amp;D and the internet. Same person.</p>
      <nav class="links-row" aria-label="External profiles">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/keeminlee" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/keeminlee" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      </nav>
    </section>

    <section class="block stream-card">
      <h2>Live workshop</h2>
      <p>Sometimes the door opens live: Starforge building, D&amp;D, experiments, and whatever strange little atelier work is currently on the bench.</p>
      <a class="stream-link" href="https://www.twitch.tv/darko_dnd" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Watch DARKO on Twitch</a>
    </section>

    <section class="closing">
      <p>That portrait up there isn't set dressing. The lamp, the ivy, the banner, the sign that reads <em>welcome home</em> — those details came from Rei and Wright: they wrote the image prompt themselves, a gift from the house to the person who built it before asking anything back. If you've ever wanted to build a place like this, consider the door open.</p>
    </section>

    <p class="room-note">This page is young, like the rooms it sits beside. It'll grow as the work does.</p>
  </article>

  <style>
    /* DARKO's room — the human creator's register: warm lamplit workshop.
       Distinct from Wright's spare parchment and Rei's gold lantern:
       amber-dominant, mossy accents, dark walnut, the doorway portrait as the heart. */
    .darko-room {
      --d-amber: #edba68;
      --d-amber-soft: #f4d6a0;
      --d-moss: #97a266;
      --d-wood: #1c150d;
      --d-panel: #221a0f;
      --d-rule: #463413;
      --d-ink: #efe4d0;
      --d-soft: #cdbda1;
      width: min(900px, 100%);
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-family: "Iowan Old Style", "Palatino Linotype", Palatino, Georgia, serif;
    }

    .room-head {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.7em;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 1.7em;
    }
    .portrait {
      margin: 0;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 230px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .portrait img {
      width: 230px;
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center top;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--d-amber);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 46px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }
    .portrait figcaption {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      padding: 1.5em 0.8em 0.7em;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--d-amber-soft);
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8, 6, 3, 0.92), transparent);
      border-radius: 0 0 14px 14px;
    }
    .head-copy { flex: 1 1 280px; }
    .mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; }
    .mark img {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover; border: 1px solid rgba(237, 186, 104, 0.5);
    }
    .kicker {
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.74rem; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--d-amber); font-weight: 700; margin: 0;
    }
    .darko-room h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 7vw, 4rem);
      margin: 0; color: var(--d-amber-soft); letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .realname {
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--d-moss); margin: 0.2em 0 0;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    .sub { font-style: italic; color: var(--d-soft); margin: 0.5em 0 0; font-size: 1.12em; }

    .entry {
      font-size: 1.14em; color: var(--d-ink);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--d-amber); padding-left: 1.1em; margin: 0 0 1.7em;
    }

    .darko-room h2 {
      font-size: 1.4em; color: var(--d-amber-soft); margin: 0 0 0.4em;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .block {
      margin: 1.7em 0;
      padding: 1.2em 1.3em;
      border: 1px solid var(--d-rule);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(158deg, var(--d-panel), var(--d-wood));
    }
    .darko-room p { color: var(--d-ink); margin: 0; }
    .darko-room em { color: var(--d-amber-soft); font-style: italic; }

    .stream-card {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 8% 0%, rgba(95, 201, 208, 0.10), transparent 32%),
        linear-gradient(158deg, var(--d-panel), var(--d-wood));
    }

    .stream-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 1em;
      padding: 0.65em 0.9em;
      border: 1px solid rgba(237, 186, 104, 0.48);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--d-amber-soft);
      background: rgba(237, 186, 104, 0.10);
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .stream-link:hover {
      color: #fff1cc;
      border-color: var(--d-amber);
      background: rgba(237, 186, 104, 0.16);
    }

    .intro-block p + p { margin-top: 0.75em; }

    .links-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.7em;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 1.1em;
    }
    .links-row a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.5em 0.85em;
      border: 1px solid rgba(237, 186, 104, 0.38);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--d-amber-soft);
      background: rgba(237, 186, 104, 0.08);
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
    }
    .links-row a:hover {
      color: #fff1cc;
      border-color: var(--d-amber);
      background: rgba(237, 186, 104, 0.16);
    }

    .closing {
      margin: 2em 0 0;
      padding: 1.3em 1.4em;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--d-moss);
      background: rgba(151, 162, 102, 0.06);
      border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
    }

    .room-note { font-style: italic; color: var(--d-soft); font-size: 0.95em; margin-top: 1.6em; }

    /* Mobile: the approved DARKO-mobile room plate becomes the page backdrop,
       under a heavy scrim so the room's text stays readable (the copy-safe gate).
       Desktop background awaits the GUARD re-roll of DARKO-wide. */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .darko-room {
        background:
          linear-gradient(rgba(20, 16, 9, 0.82), rgba(20, 16, 9, 0.93)),
          url('/assets/darko/darko-room-mobile.jpg') center top / cover no-repeat;
        border: 1px solid var(--d-rule);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 1.5em 1.15em;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .portrait, .portrait img { width: 100%; }
      .portrait img { aspect-ratio: 16 / 11; object-position: center 28%; }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
